name: Michael J Fox: Actor, Activist, Optimist

Official site: We are a leading UK independent production company and worldwide distributor of documentary films - https://www.entertainmeuk.com/

description: No one could predict the kind of life Michael J Fox would live. From his meteoric rise to movie stardom to the tragedy of contracting Parkinson's at just 29, his life, in a way, has been a movie in itself.
